init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world is now a place where the supernatural is commonplace, and where the power of Mana can be used to create magic items, summon spirits

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: o the horror of common folk who get caught up in the power struggles of those with magic, those without magic and those who want to become the most powerful being on the planet who will stop at nothing

actions.text: And the only way to do that is to find the remaining humans who are scattered all over the world and train them.
